snippet.title: Bakken - Ski Jumping: Steam Next Fest Trailer
snippet.description:
Bakken - Ski Jumping is a winter sports simulation game.

To go for gold you have to jump as high as possible, you have to fly as long as possible and
you mustn't forget the telemark landing!

#SkiJumpingIsBack


Steam Next Fest: 6 February 2023 - 13 February 2023
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2197930/Bakken__Ski_Jumping/


YouTube:
https://www.youtube.com/@bakkenvideos

Website:
https://www.bakken-skijumping.com/

Twitter:
https://twitter.com/bakkentweets


Music:
Bryan Teoh - Inventing Flight
